%E1%BB%A7/Nh%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BA%A5t/poem-qbNXQrsH_GA6BcRIN5AFDg">Nhất thất - 一室</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Th%E1%BA%A7n-%C3%94ng/S%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-thi%C3%AAn-hi%E1%BB%83u-gi%E1%BB%91c-Ho%C3%A0-trung-trai-c%E1%BB%ADu-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-wp7kssFOHHcEks8jqjb8Pw">Sương thiên hiểu giốc - Hoà trung trai cửu nhật - 霜天曉角－和中齋九日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Th%E1%BA%A7n-%C3%94ng/author-yLD6zlviNUkRwmmSAfOSjA">Lưu Thần Ông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-Giao/T%E1%BA%BF-Nguy%C3%AAn-h%C3%A0n-th%E1%BB%B1c-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-zk6XheWLgtvqx5PxHFHCcw">Tế Nguyên hàn thực kỳ 4 - 濟源寒食其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-Giao/author-lb0C1LYxo0fcanV11dmAog">Mạnh Giao</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-kh%C3%A1ch-c%E1%BA%A3m-II/poem-vEtWnUDh_HwEMjDMyqQrgg">Thu dạ khách cảm (II) - 秋夜客感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%E1%BB%A8c-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-YrFgVDhYiheqwKg7ob0-Ig">Ức đệ kỳ 1 - 憶弟其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
